[Article in Russian; Abstract available in Russian from the publisher]

Bogomolov AN(1), Imaev TE(2), Shishkevich AN(3), Komlev AE(2), Senkina EI(1), 
Lukyanov NG(3), Bashkatova LV(4), Kozlov KL(1)(3).

Author information:
(1)Saint-Petersburg Institute of Bioregulation and Gerontology, 3 pr. Dinamo, 
