Incremental cost-effectiveness of extracorporeal membranous oxygenation as a 
bridge to cardiac transplant or left ventricular assist device placement in 
patients with refractory cardiogenic shock.

Reza J(1), Mila A(1), Ledzian B(2), Sun J(3), Silvestry S(2).

