A feedback loop between lamellipodial extension and HGF-ERK signaling specifies 
leader cells during collective cell migration.

Hino N(1), Matsuda K(2), Jikko Y(3), Maryu G(4), Sakai K(5), Imamura R(5), 
Tsukiji S(6), Aoki K(7), Terai K(3), Hirashima T(8), Trepat X(9), Matsuda M(10).

